<L>__{interior. landing}
<A>__{the woman has come around to one of the three doors on the landing and is inserting a key into a lock. arnold and charlie appear now at the head of the stairway. the woman goes into her room, leaving the door open. a moment later, a shaft of light streams out into the landing. for a moment, nothing happens. then arnold and charlie amble slowly down the landing to the open doorway and shaft of light.}
