<D>__{i will wait out here for you, okay?}
<A>__{arnold nods and goes into the room. he closes the door. charlie takes out a cigarette and lights it and inhales deeply. he feels a little sordid. there is the sound of steps, muffled by the carpeting, coming down the stairs. a man appears coming down from the floor above. he gives charlie a quick look and continues on down the landing to the stairs and down again. charlie scowls at the floor. he smokes his cigarette.}
